{"word":"πρυλέες","slug":"πρυλέες","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n90830\" key=\"prule/es\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πρῠλέες</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">έων</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">οἱ</gen>, <sense id=\"n90830.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">men-at-arms, soldiers</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὐτοὶ δὲ π. σὺν τεύχεσι θωρηχθέντες</foreign>, opp. chiefs fighting from chariots, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:49\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.49</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πρώτοισι μετὰ πρυλέεσσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:90\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.90</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Λαοδάμαντα, ἡγεμόνα πρυλέων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:517\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.517</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κυνέην . . ἑκατὸν πολίων πρυλέεσσ᾽ ἀραρυῖαν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:744\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.744</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Ἄρης . . πρυλέεσσι κελεύων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg003.perseus-grc1:193\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S